{"tid":972887,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比日本還變態!？台製內褲大戰遊戲將登Switch","createTime":"2019-01-07T16:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T17:33:53.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a7e6f5bfcbbc4ad944cb787999aa978645445c7","tid":972887,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3815/e3815790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3815%2Fe3815790.jpg&h=dea0e067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被許多日本玩家稱讚「比日本人更變態了！」「台灣走在時代尖端」，由台灣獨立團隊「愛莉姆遊戲」製作的內褲戰鬥遊戲《Panty Party》即將在2019年春天推出Nintendo Switch版。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3815/e3815792.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3815%2Fe3815792.jpg&h=9c85e71a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3815/e3815791.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3815%2Fe3815791.jpg&h=120ae0f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Panty Party》在2017年1月24日於Steam平台上架發行，由於發行了多國語言版本，加上有世界知名實況主如Pewdiepie拍片，在推出之時就受到不少國外玩家關注。在遊戲中，玩家是要操作一條女用內褲去和其他內褲對戰，在遊玩過程中還會遇到各式各樣的敵人與夥伴，不管是小熊內褲、蕾絲內褲、還是純白內褲，只要女生會穿的通通都有...為了解救被變成內褲的人類而努力奮鬥著。<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/vRk_n82_Dx8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvRk_n82_Dx8&d=j9iwIuiB48CRO2cpd1IC9hFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=c566828b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vRk_n82_Dx8</a><br />\n<br />\n《Panty Party》的Nintendo Switch版將進行一些改動，包含追加新的隱藏角色（內褲）以及4人對戰模式。日本代理商同時也拍攝了宣傳影片，在登上Switch後是否可再引發一波旋風值得玩家關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OHdbPiCM1qY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOHdbPiCM1qY&d=j9iwIuiB48CRO2cpd1IC9hFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=da3d3076\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OHdbPiCM1qY</a>"},{"pid":"4765e569691da3c7f8ead2b771b7eb577b6f1341","tid":972887,"uid":150609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:59:38.000Z","msg":"任豚竟然唔和諧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c77042fcac6f177b84a8e02ca2994f079dd67a","tid":972887,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ce26cf673d47d1f96cdc5119250a6ec3bbd819","tid":972887,"uid":2994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}